byl:preamble.byl:preambletext:
WHEREAS under section 229(1) of the Local Government Act, the Board may, by
				bylaw, delegate its powers, duties and functions, including those specifically
				established by an enactment, to an officer or employee;

WHEREAS the Board of the Regional District of Nanaimo wishes to delegate to the
				General Manager of Strategic and Community Development the power under section 490
				of the Local Government Act to issue development permits;
